<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>false</action_insert><action_query>true</action_query><action_update>false</action_update><active>false</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>ecc_queue</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>Pre-G MID Upgrade ECC Blocker</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/) {
	var query = current.getEncodedQuery();
	if (query.indexOf('agent') != -1) {
		var agent = '';
		var queryArr = query.split('^');
		for (var i = 0; i < queryArr.length; i++)
			if (queryArr[i].indexOf('agent') != -1)
				agent = queryArr[i].split('=')[1];
		
		var mid = MIDServer.getByName(agent);

		if (mid && mid.isPreGeneva())
			current.addQuery('topic', 'IN', ['SystemCommand', 'HeartbeatProbe']);
	}

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>will.swift</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-03-03 23:49:05</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>2450c0003702120069da03488e41f1d5</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Pre-G MID Upgrade ECC Blocker</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="MID Server" source="com.glideapp.agent">e2a96bc5dd6003003399d83d70be0278</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_2450c0003702120069da03488e41f1d5</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2017-10-16 22:26:03</sys_updated_on><template/><when>before</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=2450c0003702120069da03488e41f1d5"/></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.bpmSignal</api_name><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><name>bpmSignal</name><script><![CDATA[var bpmSignal = Class.create();
bpmSignal.prototype = Object.extendsObject(AbstractAjaxProcessor,{
	sendSignal: function() {
		try {
			//var userRecord = new GlideRecord("sys_user");
			
			
			var myjson = this.getParameter('sysparm_jsonObj'); //paramter from the client side
			//var url = this.getParameter('sysparm_baseurl'); //paramter from the client side
			var restMessage = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2();
			//url = url + "/api/person";
			restMessage.setEndpoint('http://loopback-api-midaas-loopback-pocredhatbpmsdemo.apps.dev.ldcloud.com.au/api/bpm_signals');
			restMessage.setHttpMethod('post');
			//restMessage.setMIDServer('midserverbyname');
			restMessage.setRequestHeader('content-type','application/json');
			restMessage.setRequestHeader('accept','application/json');
			//JSON.stringfy(myjson);
			//JSUtil.describeObject(myjson);
		//	gs.addInfoMessage('<script type=text/javascript>var t=setTimeout(function(){alert("' + myjson + '")},500);</script>' + myjson);
			
			
			restMessage.setRequestBody(myjson);
			
			var response = restMessage.execute();
			var httpStatus = response.getStatusCode();
			var responseBody = response.haveError() ? response.getErrorMessage() : response.getBody();
			
			
			if (httpStatus == '200'){
				gs.info('Body: '+responseBody);
				
				
			}else{
				gs.info('HTTP Status: '+httpStatus);
				gs.info('Error: '+responseBody);
			}
			return responseBody;
		}
		catch(ex) {
			var message = ex.getMessage();
		}

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>false</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>false</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>ecc_agent</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition/><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>Disable Pre-G Blocker BR</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/) {
	if (checkAllMidsUpgraded()) {
		var eccBrGr = new GlideRecord('sys_script');
		eccBrGr.addQuery('sys_id', 'IN', ['2450c0003702120069da03488e41f1d5', '210c00803702120069da03488e41f1e4']);
		eccBrGr.setValue('active', false);
		eccBrGr.updateMultiple();
	}
})(current, previous);

function checkAllMidsUpgraded() {
	var gr = new GlideRecord('ecc_agent');
	gr.query();
	while (gr.next())
		if (MIDServer.getByName(gr.name).isPreGeneva())
			return false;
	
	return true;
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>will.swift</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-03-04 00:43:15</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>210c00803702120069da03488e41f1e4</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Disable Pre-G Blocker BR</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="MID Server" source="com.glideapp.agent">e2a96bc5dd6003003399d83d70be0278</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_210c00803702120069da03488e41f1e4</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>system</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2017-10-16 22:26:02</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=210c00803702120069da03488e41f1e4"/></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.REST_vacantrole</api_name><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><name>REST_vacantrole</name><script><![CDATA[var REST_vacantrole = Class.create();
REST_vacantrole.prototype = Object.extendsObject(AbstractAjaxProcessor, {
	restcall: function() {
		try {
			//var userRecord = new GlideRecord("sys_user");
			var myjson = this.getParameter('sysparm_jsonObj'); //paramter from the client side
			var restMessage = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2();
			myjson = JSON.parse(myjson);
			var baseLbURL= myjson.baseLbURL;
			baseLbURL = baseLbURL + '/vacantRole';
			restMessage.setEndpoint(baseLbURL);
			myjson = JSON.stringify(myjson);
			//gs.addInfoMessage(baseLbURL);
			restMessage.setHttpMethod('post');
			restMessage.setStringParameter('user_key','2e58db37ae2d7c4bdfad0c6a8885e4ce');
			//restMessage.setMIDServer('midserverbyname');
			restMessage.setRequestHeader('content-type','application/json');
			restMessage.setRequestHeader('accept','application/json');
			//JSON.stringfy(myjson);
			//JSUtil.describeObject(myjson);
			//alert(myjson);
			restMessage.setRequestBody(myjson);
			
			var response = restMessage.execute();
			var httpStatus = response.getStatusCode();
			var responseBody = response.haveError() ? response.getErrorMessage() : response.getBody();
			
			
			if (httpStatus == '200'){
				gs.info('Body: '+responseBody);
				
				
			}else{
				gs.info('HTTP Status: '+httpStatus);
				gs.info('Error: '+responseBody);
			}
			return responseBody;
		}
		catch(ex) {
			var message = ex.getMessage();
		}
	},
	type: 'REST_vacantrole'
});]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-01-04 03:53:11</sys_created_on><sys_id>9e3b1ccc0f2707002567adabe1050e20</sys_id><sys_mod_count>40</sys_mod_count><sys_name>REST_vacantrole</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_9e3b1ccc0f2707002567adabe1050e20</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-01-17 05:38:49</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_script_include_143e1ae50f23c7002567adabe1050e59
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.REST_person</api_name><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><name>REST_person</name><script><![CDATA[var REST_person = Class.create();
REST_person.prototype = Object.extendsObject(AbstractAjaxProcessor, {
	restcall: function() {
		try {
			//var userRecord = new GlideRecord("sys_user");
			var myjson = this.getParameter('sysparm_jsonObj'); //paramter from the client side
			var restMessage = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2();
			myjson = JSON.parse(myjson);
			var baseLbURL= myjson.baseLbURL;
			baseLbURL = baseLbURL + '/person';
			restMessage.setEndpoint(baseLbURL);
			delete myjson.baseLbURL;
			myjson = JSON.stringify(myjson);
			gs.addInfoMessage(baseLbURL);
			restMessage.setHttpMethod('post');
			//restMessage.setMIDServer('midserverbyname');
			restMessage.setRequestHeader('content-type','application/json');
			restMessage.setRequestHeader('accept','application/json');
			restMessage.setRequestBody(myjson);
			
			var response = restMessage.execute();
			var httpStatus = response.getStatusCode();
			var responseBody = response.haveError() ? response.getErrorMessage() : response.getBody();
			
			if (httpStatus == '200'){
				gs.info('Body: '+responseBody);
				
				
			}else{
				gs.info('HTTP Status: '+httpStatus);
				gs.info('Error: '+responseBody);
			}
			return responseBody;
		}
		catch(ex) {
			var message = ex.getMessage();
		}
	},
	type: 'REST_person'
});]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2018-01-09 05:16:32</sys_created_on><sys_id>143e1ae50f23c7002567adabe1050e59</sys_id><sys_mod_count>9</sys_mod_count><sys_name>REST_person</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_143e1ae50f23c7002567adabe1050e59</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2018-01-17 05:38:40</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
